---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for WFH Setup — rules, disclaimers, and user responsibilities when using our website, tools, and content."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: July 14, 2026</p>
        <div class="mt-10 prose prose-lg prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using WFH Setup (wfhsetup.com), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our website.
          </p>

          <h2>2. Website Purpose</h2>
          <p>
            WFH Setup provides free informational content, guides, and interactive tools related to home office setup, remote work productivity, and ergonomics. All content is for general informational purposes only and does not constitute professional advice (medical, financial, legal, or otherwise).
          </p>

          <h2>3. No Professional Advice</h2>
          <p>
            The information on this website is provided "as is" for general informational purposes. While we strive to provide accurate, up-to-date information, we make no warranties regarding completeness, accuracy, or suitability. We are not medical professionals, ergonomists, financial advisors, or legal professionals. Always consult a qualified professional for advice specific to your situation.
          </p>

          <h2>4. Interactive Tools</h2>
          <p>
            Our free interactive tools (Home Office Planner, Ergonomic Calculator, Remote Job Finder, and Productivity Scorecard) run entirely in your browser. No data you enter is transmitted to our servers, stored by us, or shared with third parties. Results are for informational purposes only and should not be relied upon as the sole basis for any decision.
          </p>

          <h2>5. Affiliate Links and Advertising</h2>
          <p>
            Some links on WFH Setup are affiliate links. If you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you. We only recommend products we genuinely believe offer value to our readers. Our participation in affiliate programs does not influence our content, reviews, or recommendations.
          </p>
          <p>
            WFH Setup also displays advertisements through Google AdSense and other advertising networks. We do not control the content of advertisements displayed. Clicking on advertisements is at your own discretion.
          </p>

          <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All original content on WFH Setup — including articles, guides, tool designs, graphics, and site layout — is owned by WFH Setup and protected by applicable copyright laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or republish our content without prior written permission. Brief excerpts with attribution and a link back to the original content are generally acceptable.
          </p>

          <h2>7. User Conduct</h2>
          <p>
            By using this website, you agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Attempt to disrupt, harm, or gain unauthorized access to the website, its servers, or its content.</li>
            <li>Use automated means (bots, scrapers) to extract content without permission.</li>
            <li>Post spam, malicious links, or unauthorized promotional content through any contact forms.</li>
            <li>Misrepresent your identity when contacting us.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>8. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>
            Our website contains links to third-party websites (product retailers, job platforms, learning resources, etc.). We are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of these external sites. Visiting third-party links is at your own risk, and you should review their respective terms and privacy policies.
          </p>

          <h2>9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, WFH Setup and its owners shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or special damages arising out of or in connection with your use of this website. This includes, but is not limited to, damages resulting from:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Reliance on information or tool results presented on this site</li>
            <li>Purchases made through affiliate links</li>
            <li>Injuries or health issues related to ergonomic or home office setup advice</li>
            <li>Technical issues, interruptions, or errors on the website</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>10. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to update these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
          </p>

          <h2>11. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms of Service are governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws. Any disputes arising from these terms shall be resolved in the appropriate jurisdiction.
          </p>

          <h2>12. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about these Terms of Service? Visit our <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a> or email <a href="mailto:hello@wfhsetup.com">hello@wfhsetup.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
